Dracona nodded.. "liono realized that nobody liked him and he kicked
everyone who doesn't like him out.....they don't have to listen any
longer..they're free to go....." Dracona said...she looked behind
her.....Plintissa was building something....Dracona, not wanting to fight
anyone, decided to go over....she walked over just a few steps....and called
out to plintissa....Plintissa pulled her blaster anmd pointed it at Dracona,
but then lowered it when she noticed that Dracona was with Silverbolt and
Teltoli..... "Dracona is with you 2?..." Plintissa said to Teltoli and
Silverbolt........
